1. offlineimap/ contains configuration information pertaining to the
   `offlineimap` utility, used to sync emails

2. mu/ has configuration and maildir index files used by `mu`

3. maildirs/ contains the actual Maildir directories for each mailbox synced
   by hipflask-mail

4. sqlite/ has the SQLite db containing user and account information

Because git cannot store empty folders, these directories are created if they
do not already exist based on config.py
